Connectivity Technology Wireless
Special Feature 2-Way Audio, Night Vision, Motion Sensor

About this item

  • AI-Powered Human Recognition & AlertsAn integrated PIR motion sensor delivers precise real-time notifications upon detecting movement. Thanks to AI-enabled human detection, only alerts related to human activity will trigger notifications, eliminating false alarms caused by pets or vehicles.
  • 2-Way Communication & Shared AccessStay in touch with your loved ones with real-time two-way audio, accessible from anywhere. Share camera access with family members for concurrent remote monitoring. The two-way audio feature activates only when the doorbell button is pressed.
  • 1080p & Infrared Night VisionWith this outdoor security camera, enjoy 1080p Full HD visuals and infrared night vision, empowering you to oversee your home throughout the day and night, regardless of your location.
  • All-Weather DurabilityWith IP65 dustproof and waterproof certification, this camera delivers year-round security, irrespective of the weather conditions.
  • Secure Cloud StorageProtect your footage with AES-128 encrypted cloud storage. Opt for a subscription plan (sold separately) for advanced security, including video preservation, missed event reviews, and video sharing. Benefit from a 30-day free trial included with your purchase.

    How customer reviews and ratings work

    Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

    To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.
